How to start cron job


sudo service cron  start
crontab -e


nano houselink.cron
(i to insert)* 12 * * * python3 right_move_houselink_correct_17_02.py
Ctrl+o( for save purpose)
after enter
Ctrl+X
crontab house_link.cron
crontab -l (for load purpose)
wait for program run.



nano train_notification.cron
(i to insert)* 7,15 * * * python3 Train_4in1_working_6_1.py
Ctrl+o( for save purpose)
after enter
Ctrl+X
crontab train_notification.cron
crontab -l (for load purpose)
wait for program run.	 
